Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在期望着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望有一天自己能够成为特别的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望有一天能够找到会认可自己才能的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在很久以前我就一直想象自己是一位守护在公主身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历了无数战斗的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  看来我错过了那趟梦想的列车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是我最喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静  没有人流的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合一个人看书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  今天却有一位客人捷足先登了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个车站是没有电车的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我第一次和她相遇的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一次不足四十五秒的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不出去取材一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  是景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥可别忘记参加晚会哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便去露个脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到好画面了吗  京介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只拍好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实下雪就最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  拼接场景的时候就够呛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了  反正也是取材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  只是觉得把宣传海报拍下来也不错的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是看到好女孩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又来了  又来了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  欢迎回来  景学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕店人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  哥哥人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  他到底还要不要来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟他说了这次再放鸽子就绝对不会放过他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纮学长好像总是那么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有参加社团活动也没有上补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有别的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希来帮我摆放一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我还以为他在想事情  结果突然发疯似的挠头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像是在最后期限前赶工的漫画家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  景学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再发次短信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像来得有点晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来里面是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥撒仪式已经结束了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我并不是教徒  只是想来取材
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个非见不可的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢  现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  景这家伙生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  那边的人  你看见一辆摩托车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他往哪边跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  这个借我下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这自行车小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么喂喂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  哥哥你该不会把晚会的事给忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是放鸽子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有去舞蹈会的礼服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白雪公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我现在是灰姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在没空和你扯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  难道突然接到工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再联络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说下次再联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥那个笨蛋  去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,119吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车来之后  我还要陪她一起去医院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么问我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不安分点躺着怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我东西被偷了  我最重要的挎包被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撞到头的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是等救护车来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那挎包很贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面还有钱包和手机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要抓住那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜里的公园还真能让人平静下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小偷怎么了  不是说一定要把他抓到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑得太久  累死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃得也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正钱包里面又没有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话里面也只有奶奶家的电话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个挎包也差不多想换了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才说的差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么疼的地方  或者是想吐的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没有  完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是本人感觉不到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟晕了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一下子失去了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  完全没有一点记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  不可能有人在晕过去以后还知道自己在干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能为我担心  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说  说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  总之还是去一趟医院比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是雪  下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得这样也很不错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和别人一起的白色圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也  也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  太冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的日子一个人过的话太孤单了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我就算一个人也可以活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不大喜欢一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没告诉你我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宫村宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是广野纮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广野纮  是广纮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫村宫子  宫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  说起来还真是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你发现有趣的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  广野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家里今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在想色色的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛  家里的钥匙也都在那个挎包里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样  就算回到家也进不了门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就要露宿街头了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一个女孩子在外面通宵的话不是很不安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  要我陪你一起露宿街头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说  一不做二不休
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}等一下  我才不要和你  我还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今年的圣诞节要结束  还早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:31.21,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:31.21,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}理想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在放学的班会上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发下来了志愿调查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同于小时候憧憬的未来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要具体地确定自己的将来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成为在灾难中为保护公主而战的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是可以写那种梦想的岁数了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我错过了那趟梦想的列车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  为什么要来问我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听听成年人的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果是火村先生的话  可能会给我什么好建议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  我既不是牧师也不是心理咨询师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你一直待在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪我要和你商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要在这里等人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有喜欢的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的东西吗？  读书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢读小说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去读文科大学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去做与出版社有关的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以自己写小说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  把喜欢的事情变为职业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是太武断了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比把讨厌的事情变为工作好上千倍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要烦恼了  好好考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的成人的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成年人的…意见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得似懂非懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正说到底  还是要自己考虑是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得那么简单…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.15,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.15,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}思念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是妨碍到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我可以问你一个奇怪的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前和我见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我们是见过面的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  其实也只是一面之缘而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:14:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你经常来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只是偶尔来而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很安静  是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这里真是个得天独厚的读书的好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  还能体验Stand  by  Me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}注：出自1986年的一部美国电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在铁路上走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在这里玩的话没人会骂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是新藤千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子会把孩子推进千寻的山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写法就是这个千寻  读作chihiro
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是麻生莲治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麻生同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  上次也是你比我先来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有去学校上学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有去  学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里明明是麻生同学的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里会给你添麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得你好像有点平静不下来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在考虑和你同样的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为我在这里  让千寻不能安静地读书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有那么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我还想在这里待一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天已经黑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  还能再到这里来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  再见…啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.60,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.60,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没有看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  是指什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  我只是觉得你和昨天有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  难道你是麻生同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的「再见」…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「再见」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你怎么了  千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不是那样的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  哎呀  我  为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我为什么也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  为什么今天麻生同学你会来到这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不知不觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太高兴了  一下子误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  真的  请你忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  见到我她很高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  明明只见过三次面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至于抱着我哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是我最近在读的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢小说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就好像文字中毒一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口袋里经常放了几本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没带书的话  就好像重量少了  会感觉很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是猫的胡子一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻的那本书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是猫的胡子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个的话我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你和我一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生同学  我有一个请求  你能答应我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能和我  成为朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是  想让你成为我的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生同学说完这句话以后回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生同学和昨天的我约定好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来和今天的我见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我  也和他约定好了明天再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  他还和这样的我成为了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想好了  不能为了这种事而放纵自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人再度相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惘的时间又再一次开始转动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  ef  -  a  tale  of  memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不愿忘却的回忆吗
